Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.07,0:00:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When were the Taika Reforms?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.15,0:00:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in third grade; you should know already! You're so dumb.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't learned it yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call them the "uneventful reforms".
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.65,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: The word translated here as "uneventful" is mujiko. The\Nnumbers 6, 2, and 5 can be pronounced as mu, ji, and ko respectively.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.02,0:00:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneventful?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see, nothing much happened during them.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneventful six-two-five.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneventful... six-two-five.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it stuck in my head now,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry.
Comment: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:40.43,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{Op Keyframe}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:41.11,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HF1DEEB&}Just who are we letting grow up on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:42.14,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.46,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}Never, never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.79,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:45.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}Never give up!
