Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.13,0:00:55.35,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}{\pos(640,110)\bord6\shad0\3c&HFFFFFF&}Idiots and Tests and Summoned Beings
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.13,0:00:55.35,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}{\pos(639,109)\be1}Idiots and Tests and Summoned Beings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.29,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFF3BA&}Meeting someone else is the easy way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.95,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HEBD5FE&}I knew what I would say before they even asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.49,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HB1FFB2&}Do I look lovestruck enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.72,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HC9E4FF&}I'm not gonna lose my cool, love's at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.75,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCAC7FF&}Study! Study! Study! It keeps me up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.39,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFC9EB&}I've got a genius inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:14.97,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HA0E6FF&}It'd be great if my dreams came true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.22,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD6C3CB&}because I don't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:19.83,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD5CDFF&}Perfect area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:22.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCDFFDC&}I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:29.11,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFFED3&}I can hear your voice from the perfect area ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.42,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HE8D4FF&}Fly! I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.34,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HBBECFF&}Yeah, that's me, the person you just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.64,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFCABF&}Are we still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.82,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HABFFC7&}I flunked our friendship test, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:44.14,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&H889DF8&}No! I'll take it again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.25,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFD8BF&}Come on, gimme another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:50.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFEBBF&}Something better awaits us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:57.08,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD7C3FD&}A better life awaits us!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.59,0:02:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here at Fumizuki Academy, knowledge is power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:37.13,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(913,489)}{\c&H6AFA85&}Second Period\N{\c&HD16AD6&}Lilies and Roses and Health
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and your test score is justice.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Himeji?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.87,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got something for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanted to ask you about something...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a moment?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.29,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class F ended up winning the first sophomore ESB.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're better than I thought.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.36,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The class that lost to them must be angry about having their facilities downgraded.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.63,0:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe that'll teach them that they\Nneed to study hard in order to win battles.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life itself is a battle, after a-
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The students personally requested that they not swap facilities.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't called superglue for nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're as good as new in no time flat.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.64,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should feel blessed that we're afforded the luxury of such high quality glue.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.23,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to upgrade your\Nsupplies after winning a tough battle.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.98,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, but we could be using class E's desks right now...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, why the hell did you turn down the trade?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, man?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like those shitty desks?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.08,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're better than these damn flimsy tables!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.43,0:04:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't study anyway, so what difference does it make to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big one!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I eat on it, I sleep on it, and I draw on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.23,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\b1\bord0\c&H200F1E&\fnMarker SD\pos(536,150)\frz2.023}Mizuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.23,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\b1\bord0\c&H200F1E&\fnMarker SD\pos(754,145)\frz1.512}Akihisa
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, my desk is an important part of my school experience!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They share the same heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last day we'll be using them.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.95,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class A declared war on us, yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna beat them and start using their facilities.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation's not exactly what I had in mind, but we should do just fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My predictions allowed for a certain margin of error.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Himeji?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.19,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go to class A.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.92,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is class A.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks more like a five star hotel.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.04,0:04:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I should be spending my school days!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.26,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, Yoshii! They have a self-serving bar with snacks!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.12,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get taken advantage of if that's all it takes to impress you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.54,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice what you preach.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Isn't the ESB tomorrow?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.78,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrendering already?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just here to check out our new facilities.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh, so tough.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to negotiate.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a one-on-one battle\Nbetween the two class reps.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.10,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think you can handle our class valedictorian?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.35,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but think that you're trying to take us\Nout while we're still recovering from the last ESB.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go now?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.90,0:05:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with one-on-one.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rep!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a condition.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.62,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The loser must promise to comply with an order from the winner.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was why you declared war on us?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.78,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an obligation to protect the\Npublic order and dignity of our school.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.71,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must punish lazy idiots who\Ndeclare war without doing anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.90,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. The loser of the one-on-one will do whatever the winner says.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll be five-on-five.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.13,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.29,0:06:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying that I think our rep is going to lose.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to take some precautions, is all.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Five-on-five it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.00,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, however, we'll pick the subjects.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiation complete.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We're still gonna win.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's changed is that we get the honor of bossing them around.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we should go through with this.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.35,0:06:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard some nasty rumors about Shouko Kirishima, class A's rep.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.34,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart and she's not half-bad looking either.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.93,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she doesn't have a boyfriend or\Nanything. Never even hangs out with guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she does seem like the popular type.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.58,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the rumors say she has no interest in guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No interest in-?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit, so her goal is...!?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No frickin' way.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.40,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that could be\Nhappening right under our noses.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shimada?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.33,0:07:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure it could be happening.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu!?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.62,0:07:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you drink tea with these disgusting faggots instead of hanging out with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Get the hell offa me!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.36,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.74,0:07:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu Shimizu of class 2D.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Get the hell away from me!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so shy, mistress.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.44,0:07:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you love me - you don't need to hide it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a dyke!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out here, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.63,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Shimizu. Being gay is wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.55,0:08:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While it's true that Shimada looks like a guy, acts like a guy, and has the chest of a guy...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's a pro wrestler in disguise!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally feminine in all areas!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! I love my mistress's feminine traits!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-almost...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada, stop! I'll do whatever you say!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.33,0:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want you to treat me to\Ncrepes at Lapelle's next weekend.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda low on cash-
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll treat you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you have to call me "honey" from now on.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll call you Aki.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, honey!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... And...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-say you love me!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-s...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-almost...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and say you love me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hurry up and say you love me"!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.05,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.78,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,N-n-no! You're gonna break it!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I thought I was toast.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Himeji?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like a love letter.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.73,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But who would write a love letter in the classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.89,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Get a clue. What else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.44,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\bord0\fs30\c&H1A2B56&\fnMarker SD\pos(334,156)}I finally realized
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.44,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\bord0\fs30\c&H1A2B56&\fnMarker SD\pos(334,335)}that I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Umm... I think you have the wrong idea about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:51.77,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}The proof is right in your hands.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Actually, maybe not...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But no, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:57.45,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Come on, just admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.90,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\be1\bord0\fs100\c&H1A2B56&\fnMarker SD\pos(1165,228)}...love you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What a depressing chain letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.95,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}God dammit, just deal with it!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.17,0:10:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Things will get weird if you misunderstand.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is he in our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.66,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Yuuji is in our class, obviously.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:08.96,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}There's no point in forcing yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, I'll teach you how to write depressing chain mail properly.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, this isn't a chain letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:16.22,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Do you even know how!?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.76,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Because the world is crashing down around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:24.60,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Have some tea and calm down.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seriously? What do you see in him?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's not even good-looking.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, it's not about his looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:39.28,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I mean, I like how he looks!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.55,0:10:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My friend told me that when two handsome guys like you and Sakamoto walk together,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}it's like a painting.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She sounds like a great friend. Treat her well.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She also told me that you're the bottom in the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.11,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Yuuji is definitely a better fit for Himeji.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't think you should be friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:50.37,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Maybe I still have a chance.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.11,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But he's also beautiful on the inside!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah, his liver is pretty solid.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not talking about his organs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.79,Mental Blogging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}Are you really that far in denial?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can't be telling me that you like his personality.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.97,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. He's so kind and cheerful.\NThere's always a smile on his face.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always admired him.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you hear the reply you wanted to.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to begin our strategy meeting.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going? Akihisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't walk with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the bottom!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin round one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:38.71,Text Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(299,125)}Elites vs. Idiots
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the round girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Round one.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one more suited for it than you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not a girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would both contestants please step forward?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Shimada.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off I go.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.18,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this quick. I don't feel like prolonging a battle with someone who's going to lose anyway.{she has no chance to survive make her time, etc.}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in for a shock if you think I'm weak just 'cause I'm in class F.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.94,0:12:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.82,0:12:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My math is at class B level.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no way...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.48,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in class A, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.61,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victor: Yuuko Kinoshita of class A.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not an unexpected turn of events.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.12,0:12:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you forgot that class A is higher than class B-
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-almost...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.48,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of enjoying this.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Round two.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's commence with round two.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would both contestants please step forward?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm class A's Miho Satou.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all you, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? We're screwed if we lose this one.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that. I believe in you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.12,0:13:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to get serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop hiding it now.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.27,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show everyone your true strength.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you don't make it easy for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You'll be the first to see my true power.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really are...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.62,0:13:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always kept it a secret, but I'm actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,left-handed.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victor: Miho Satou of class A.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.50,0:13:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell does being left-handed have to do with your test scores!?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-almost...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's when it really starts.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get serious.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I thought you said you believed in me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that you'd lose!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna punch you in the balls with my left hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Round three.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Round three will now begin.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class A: Aiko Kudou.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class F: Kouta Tsuchiya.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What subject?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Health.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're pretty good with health.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.81,0:14:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm pretty good at it too - in a different way.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use the knowledge {\i1}practically{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practically?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:24.34,Text Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\pos(354,144)}Carnivore vs. Voyeur
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.56,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to Voyeur!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheapskate!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sub for him?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can tell that you're hopeless, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.09,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can teach you health if you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Practically{\i0}, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.35,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.40,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business! He's never gonna get the chance to do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.87,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! He doesn't need the knowledge!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that!?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.84,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let the battle commence.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 400?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.46,0:15:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practical vs. theoretical. I'll show you which is stronger.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Mr. Voyeur.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceleration...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...complete.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victor: Kouta Tsuchiya of class F.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.14,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! His health score is on par with my comprehensive score!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin round four.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Round four.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish me luck.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Himeji!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.12,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be her opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshimitsu Kubo, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the key round.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's #2 in our year.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be tough if we don't pick something he's bad at.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what subject?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comprehensive.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we have the right to decide-
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.44,0:16:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comprehensive basically means that your class rank translates directly into your strength.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start battle.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those points.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.18,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how strong #2 is?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.08,0:16:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 4000?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her points are on par with the valedictorian.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the hell did you...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.95,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been wondering why we\Neven had ESBs in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:17:02.70,Sign Whatever,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(125,580)\frz59.626}Imagination
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.18,0:16:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this class...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.68,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because everyone helps each other out with all they have...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the person I like is in this class.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.89,0:16:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't let you guys down!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victor: Mizuki Himeji of class F.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that, Aki?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an even split now!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.27,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next match will determine everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Round five.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin the last round.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally my turn.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch and learn.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm class F's rep, Yuuji Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.63,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm class A's rep, Shouko Kirishima.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What subject?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.14,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose a restricted Japanese\Nhistory test for the final round.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.87,0:17:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The material will be of the elementary school level. The maximum points will be 100.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A testing showdown!?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a Being battle?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.41,0:17:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ESB is a battle utilizing your test scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:51.38,Text Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,105)}What's a test showdown?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it involves tests in some ways and is approved by a teacher,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't matter how you go about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Prepare yourselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both contestants, please head to the classroom.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.28,0:18:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't both of you get 100s if it's at an elementary school level?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it just going to end in a draw?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. A simple mistake means you lose it all.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.92,0:18:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a test of endurance and concentration, not academics.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.11,0:18:25.58,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it. I have this in the bag.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Shouko memorizes\Nsomething, she'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean you're at a disadvantage, then? You're dealing with history.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's the point.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.40,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She memorized the Taika Reforms as taking place in the year 625.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that question appears on the test, victory is mine.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Taika Reforms {\i1}did{\i0} take place in the year 625.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they took place in 645.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.32,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those system desks are ours.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.06,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.01,0:19:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if that question doesn't appear?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.03,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if his endurance and concentration aren't as good as hers, then we'll lose.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.68,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it does appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.72,Test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)}Please answer the following questions:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.73,Test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(640,625)}Who did Oda Nobunaga make an alliance with in the Battle of Nagashino?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:33.77,Test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(640,625)}Who signed the Harris Treaty with American Consul General Harris?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:49.29,Test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(640,625)}When did the Taika Reforms take place?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall hereby announce the scores for the restricted exam.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class A representative, Shouko Kirishima:
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,97 points.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't ace it!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna live like kings!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, class F's rep, Yuuji Sakamoto:
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,53 points.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.01,0:20:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class F ended up trading their coffee tables for cardboard boxes.
Comment: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:37.54,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Ending Keyframe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.86,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}It's a time of peace now that school's out.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.96,0:20:52.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}If I were to describe her, she's a real angel!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}Then came a notice that shattered my fun.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.67,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}It said I had to stay afterschool! It's like hell!!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}I was talking about it with my friends, and I said,
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}"No way anyone's that stupid!!"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.14,0:21:08.06,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}But deep inside me,
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.56,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}I was shouting out,
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.77,0:21:12.31,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}"I AM THAT STUPID!"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.44,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}That sign in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.90,0:21:18.65,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}that says "Monthly"...{or "Tsukigime"}
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.01,0:21:24.14,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}I always thought that was the company's name.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.79,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.50,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Stupidity's a character! A real man!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.43,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Our common sense is the lack thereof!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}We don't need rules in our fucking world!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.83,0:21:39.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}Eat steak out every night, overthrow the mass!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.92,0:21:45.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Take a look, the sun that rose from the west is setting back down!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.94,0:21:49.00,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Run home, it's almost dinner!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.66,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.03,0:21:55.72,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.53,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're even worse off than before!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was with that score!?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.13,0:22:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my ability.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.92,0:22:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you couldn't get 100, then what the hell was the point?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.05,0:22:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought there'd be an ambush.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.12,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ambush!?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.90,0:22:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:22.79,0:22:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised to comply with their order if we lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, what is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:29.75,0:22:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this, Kirishima!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.35,0:22:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homosexuality is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:35.45,0:22:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, go out with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.58,0:22:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:43.15,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.17,0:22:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I refuse?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we promised.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:50.12,0:22:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on a date right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.79,0:22:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai-
Dialogue: 5,0:22:59.06,0:23:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.10,0:23:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:02.73,0:23:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kirishima only kept staring at Himeji because...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.21,0:23:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to make sure Himeji wasn't doing anything funny with Yuuji.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, Himeji.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.04,0:23:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our classroom sucks even more than before.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:15.54,0:23:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is a fabulous room.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.80,0:23:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love class F!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:22.68,0:23:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:25.84,0:23:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Aki. You're going to treat me to some crepes.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:29.70,0:23:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I thought we were\Ngonna go on this weekend...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weekends are weekends. Today is today.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.79,0:23:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that I have to treat you twice!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have any money left to feed\Nmyself until my parents send me more!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.33,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:40.27,0:23:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to watch a movie with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.18,0:23:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember agreeing to that...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I just decided on it.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you're treating me to crepes!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What movie are we going to watch?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.46,0:23:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:56.66,0:23:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My living expenses! My nutrition! Save me!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:59.45,0:24:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Wait, my hands are going to break!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.08,0:24:04.15,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to wonder if he's really an idiot or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.05,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question three:
Dialogue: 5,0:24:07.09,0:24:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the ratio of one's income spent on food known as?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:11.82,0:24:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna be able to afford\Nanything except salt and water this week.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:13.48,0:24:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question didn't ask you what you're going to eat.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.43,0:24:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Food Expenses and Dates and Stun Guns.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:17.44,0:24:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on your test.